txt.en: While exploring Thuringwath, you have encountered what you can only presume to be a huorn-wight. Its branches withered and marked with decay, this shambling terror's eyes gleam in the darkness of Thuringwath.\n\nYou should defeat the huorn-wights of Thuringwath.
You have defeated many huorn-wights in Thuringwath.
Terrible huorn-wights lurk in the shadows of Thuringwath.
You have triumphed over the perils of the dead forest of Thuringwath and defeated many of the huorn-wights that dwell in its shadows.
Huorn-wights can be found within the white forest of Thuringwath.\n\nYou should defeat the huorn-wights lurking within Thuringwath.
